ON ANOTHER SWEATER?

00:08.842 --> 00:11.553
- I'M WEARING FIVE.
- FIVE?

00:11.636 --> 00:15.140
- I'M LIKE A RUSSIAN DOLL
UP IN HERE.

00:15.223 --> 00:17.934
- I HAVE GOT
A FANTASTIC ANNOUNCEMENT.

00:18.017 --> 00:19.936
NOW THAT I'M A GAY CELEBRITY,

00:20.019 --> 00:23.565
{\an1}I'VE BEEN INVITED TO GIVE A TALK
ON AN EXCLUSIVE LESBIAN CRUISE

00:23.648 --> 00:26.609
TO THE CARIBBEAN.

00:26.693 --> 00:27.736
- HOW'S THE FOOD?

00:27.819 --> 00:29.320
- WELL, HOW WOULD I KNOW?

00:29.404 --> 00:31.573
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
HOW THE FOOD IS HERE.

00:31.656 --> 00:34.242
- ARE YOU ONE OF THOSE PEOPLE
THAT GOES CRAZY FOR CRUISE FOOD?

00:34.325 --> 00:38.163
- I'VE BEEN ON SIX CRUISES.
NEVER SEEN THE OCEAN.

00:40.707 --> 00:42.751
- OH, WHO CARES ABOUT FOOD?

00:42.834 --> 00:45.295
THE MOST POWERFUL GAY WOMEN
IN HOLLYWOOD WILL BE LISTENING

00:45.378 --> 00:48.339
AS I SHARE MY INSPIRING STORY

00:48.423 --> 00:53.470
OF FALLING IN LOVE
AND MARRYING JOY.

00:53.553 --> 00:55.722
- BUT IT'S ALL A LIE.

00:55.805 --> 00:57.807
- YOU KNOW, A STORY DOESN'T HAVE
TO BE TRUE TO BE INSPIRING.

00:57.891 --> 01:01.978
I MEAN,<i> TITANIC</i> PROVED THAT.

01:02.061 --> 01:04.313
- MY CAR GOT STUCK
IN A SNOWDRIFT.

01:04.397 --> 01:06.941
- SO? THERE'S ALWAYS SOME GUY
THAT'LL HELP US GET IT OUT.

01:07.025 --> 01:08.693
- AND THERE WAS.
AND HE WAS CUTE.

01:08.777 --> 01:10.528
AND HE ASKED ME OUT.

01:10.612 --> 01:13.782
BUT I HAD TO SAY NO
BECAUSE I'M MARRIED TO YOU.

01:13.865 --> 01:16.117
I WANT A DIVORCE.

01:16.201 --> 01:19.662
- AND YOU SHALL HAVE ONE AFTER
I HAVE SQUEEZED EVERY LAST DROP

01:19.746 --> 01:22.457
OF ADVANTAGE
OUT OF THIS MARRIAGE.

01:22.540 --> 01:24.125
AND TO SAY THANK YOU,

01:24.209 --> 01:28.588
I AM TAKING YOU
ON A CARIBBEAN CRUISE.

01:28.671 --> 01:30.507
- REALLY?

01:30.590 --> 01:35.386
'CAUSE I'VE HEARD CRUISES
ARE GREAT PLACES TO MEET MEN.

01:35.470 --> 01:37.597
- THEY OFTEN ARE,

01:37.680 --> 01:39.140
