05:13.688 --> 05:19.068
- IF SHE ISN'T, I OWE HER
AN APOLOGY FOR LAST NIGHT.

05:19.152 --> 05:21.279
- MELANIE, WE HAVE SO MUCH
TO TALK ABOUT.

05:21.362 --> 05:24.073
SO MUCH TIME TO MAKE UP FOR.

05:24.157 --> 05:26.034
WE FINALLY HAVE
SOMETHING IN COMMON.

05:26.117 --> 05:28.953
THIS CHANGES EVERYTHING!

05:31.122 --> 05:34.083
[knocking at door]

05:34.167 --> 05:35.918
- CAPTAIN LEBEAU.

05:36.002 --> 05:37.712
WHAT AN UNEXPECTED PLEASURE.

05:37.795 --> 05:40.423
- I TRY.

05:40.506 --> 05:42.425
I WANT TO INVITE
BOTH OF YOU TO DINE WITH ME

05:42.508 --> 05:43.760
AT THE CAPTAIN'S TABLE
TONIGHT.

05:43.843 --> 05:45.053
- OF COURSE.
WHAT TIME?

05:45.136 --> 05:45.970
- 2100 HOURS?

05:46.054 --> 05:48.973
- FROM NOW?

05:49.057 --> 05:52.935
- NO.

05:53.019 --> 05:55.563
NO.
2100 IS MILITARY TIME.

05:55.646 --> 05:58.107
IT IS THE SAME AS
TWO BELLS ON THE FIRST WATCH.

05:58.191 --> 06:01.903
- WELL, THAT CLARIFIES
IT HANDSOMELY.

06:01.986 --> 06:03.071
- VICTORIA,
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

06:03.154 --> 06:04.822
- WHAT, NOW?
- YES, PLEASE.

06:04.906 --> 06:08.785
- OH, ALL RIGHT.
I--I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

06:11.913 --> 06:13.956
- SO, IT IS JUST US.

06:14.040 --> 06:15.458
-<i> OUI.</i>

06:15.541 --> 06:19.170
- SORRY.
JUST--JUST WE.

06:24.300 --> 06:26.427
- CAPTAIN, IF I TOLD YOU
SOMETHING PERSONAL,

06:26.511 --> 06:28.304
