06:28.387 --> 06:30.932
- IT WOULD BE PROTECTED
BY CAPTAIN-PASSENGER PRIVILEGE.

06:31.015 --> 06:34.143
- I'VE HEARD OF IT.

06:34.227 --> 06:36.312
