06:36.395 --> 06:39.482
I'M NOT GAY.

06:39.565 --> 06:42.276
- I SENSED THAT.

06:42.360 --> 06:45.863
- I'M TRYING TO MAKE YOU
SENSE THAT.

06:45.947 --> 06:49.325
- YOU'VE DONE IT
SUCCESSFULLY.

06:49.408 --> 06:54.330
- THERE'S SOMETHING ELSE
I'D LIKE TO DO SUCCESSFULLY.

06:54.413 --> 06:55.832
BUT NOT NOW.

06:55.915 --> 06:59.502
OH.

06:59.585 --> 07:02.338
