IS GETTING A MASSAGE.

07:02.421 --> 07:05.258
- SO NEITHER OF YOU KNEW
THE OTHER ONE WAS GAY?

07:05.341 --> 07:08.678
- I'M NOT GAY.

07:08.761 --> 07:10.847
