CHANCE TO CONNECT WITH HER,

07:10.930 --> 07:13.850
AND I'M AFRAID IF SHE FINDS OUT
IT'S A LIE, SHE'LL HATE ME.

07:13.933 --> 07:16.227
- WELL, FOR NOW, BUILD TRUST
WITH YOUR SISTER,

07:16.310 --> 07:20.189
