IF I HAVE A GIRLFRIEND?

07:23.109 --> 07:25.027
- WELL, TELL HER YOU DO.

07:25.111 --> 07:28.656
- WELL, WHO WOULD I GET TO
PRETEND TO BE MY GIRLFRIEND?

07:37.957 --> 07:41.043
- YOU'RE NOT REALLY MY TYPE.

07:45.173 --> 07:47.383
- VICTORIA, I JUST WANT
TO SAY GOOD-BYE.

07:47.466 --> 07:48.843
I WILL SEE YOU TONIGHT
AT DINNER.

07:48.926 --> 07:51.512
- I'LL SEE YOU OUT.

07:51.596 --> 07:56.017
UH, JOY? MELANIE NEEDS
SOME GAY ADVICE.

07:56.100 --> 07:57.560
- WELL, WHY CAN'T
YOU HELP HER?

07:57.643 --> 08:00.563
- WELL, YOU'RE A LITTLE
GAYER THAN I AM.

08:00.646 --> 08:03.065
