REALLY NEEDS YOU.

08:03.149 --> 08:08.279
- I'LL SEE YOU LATER, CAPTAIN.
[giggles]

08:08.362 --> 08:13.075
- SO, IT IS JUST WE.

08:13.159 --> 08:15.411
I SENSE SOMETHING ABOUT YOU.

08:15.494 --> 08:16.537
YOU'RE NOT GAY.

08:16.621 --> 08:18.456
- HOW DARE YOU!

08:18.539 --> 08:22.460
OH.

08:22.543 --> 08:25.254
- DON'T WORRY, LITTLE BIRD.
YOUR SECRET IS SAFE.

08:25.338 --> 08:28.758
PROTECTED BY
CAPTAIN-PASSENGER PRIVILEGE.

08:28.841 --> 08:31.260
- I'VE HEARD OF IT.

08:31.344 --> 08:33.554
- PERHAPS YOU SWING BOTH WAYS.

08:33.638 --> 08:38.308
- HMM, PERHAPS I SWING ONE WAY
AND THEN TOWARD YOU.

08:40.519 --> 08:42.605
- PERHAPS, YOU WOULD LIKE
TO SWING BY MY CABIN LATER.

08:42.688 --> 08:47.944
- PERHAPS I'D LIKE THAT
VERY MUCH.

08:48.027 --> 08:51.072
- SHALL WE SAY 1700 HOURS?

08:51.155 --> 08:52.949
- 1700 HOURS.

08:56.702 --> 09:00.957
