WHEN IS THAT?

09:06.587 --> 09:08.005
- CAN'T BELIEVE THE TWO OF YOU
GREW UP IN THE SAME HOUSE,

09:08.089 --> 09:09.006
AND YOU DIDN'T KNOW
THE OTHER ONE WAS GAY.

09:09.090 --> 09:10.591
- I HAD NO CLUE.

09:10.675 --> 09:13.803
- I HAD A FEW.

09:13.886 --> 09:15.846
- YOU DID?

09:15.930 --> 09:17.848
- OH, YOUR DATES--THEY WERE
ALWAYS SO UNCOMFORTABLE

09:17.932 --> 09:18.975
AROUND YOU.

09:19.058 --> 09:20.351
- NO, THEY WEREN'T.

09:20.434 --> 09:22.186
I WAS REALLY GOOD
AT PASSING FOR STRAIGHT.

09:22.270 --> 09:25.106
- AND DIDN'T YOU PLAY TRUMPET
IN MARCHING BAND?

09:25.189 --> 09:26.023
- DOESN'T MEAN ANYTHING.

09:26.107 --> 09:29.485
- YEAH, RIGHT.

09:29.568 --> 09:31.696
- I CAN'T WAIT TO MEET
YOUR GIRLFRIEND.

09:31.779 --> 09:34.991
[laughs]

09:35.074 --> 09:38.661
- HI, LOVER.

09:38.744 --> 09:41.998
- HI...LOVER.

09:42.081 --> 09:44.041
ELKA, THIS IS MY SISTER,
CAROLINE,

09:44.125 --> 09:45.001
AND HER GIRLFRIEND, NAN.

09:45.084 --> 09:50.339
AND THIS IS MY ELKA.

09:50.423 --> 09:54.468
- WOW. I HAVE
SO MANY QUESTIONS.

09:56.304 --> 10:01.017
- I'M RICH.

10:01.100 --> 10:03.394
- NO MORE QUESTIONS.

10:03.477 --> 10:07.690
- PLUS, THE SEX
IS AMAZING.

10:13.821 --> 10:15.364
- [woman over P.A.]
ATTENTION.

10:15.448 --> 10:17.533
