THE FOLLOWING YEAR.

10:35.134 --> 10:37.928
- BUT THEY'RE HAPPY,
AND THAT'S WHAT MATTERS.

10:38.012 --> 10:41.223
- OR MAYBE WHAT MATTERS IS THAT
OUR GLASSES ARE EMPTY.

10:41.307 --> 10:44.894
- OKAY, I'LL GET US
ANOTHER ROUND.

10:44.977 --> 10:48.147
HEY, I SAY WE GET
A LITTLE PLASTERED,

10:48.230 --> 10:50.066
