10:52.193 --> 10:57.740
- [forced laugh]

10:57.823 --> 11:01.243
- SO ARE YOU REALLY HAPPY
WITH ELKA?

11:01.327 --> 11:03.204
- OH, YEAH, FOR SURE.

11:03.287 --> 11:05.414
- 'CAUSE AFTER ALL THOSE YEARS
OF SETTLING FOR A MAN,

11:05.498 --> 11:07.583
