TO SETTLE AGAIN.

11:07.666 --> 11:10.920
- WELL, YOU KNOW, I WOULDN'T
CALL IT "SETTLING."

11:11.003 --> 11:13.714
- SO PRETTY.

11:13.798 --> 11:17.635
IF YOU WERE MY WOMAN, I'D NEVER
LEAVE YOU FOR A SHRIMP BAR.

11:21.514 --> 11:25.226
- OKAY.

11:25.309 --> 11:28.312
- AHOY, CAPTAIN.

11:28.396 --> 11:30.064
- OH, THANK GOD YOU'RE HERE.

11:30.147 --> 11:31.273
CAROLINE'S GIRLFRIEND
JUST HIT ON ME.

11:31.357 --> 11:33.275
HIT ON ME--
I NEED A PLAN.

11:33.359 --> 11:34.610
- JUST TELL YOUR SISTER
THE TRUTH.

11:34.693 --> 11:37.113
SHE'LL UNDERSTAND.
NOW OFF YOU GO.

11:37.196 --> 11:39.240
- I KNOW, BUT WHAT IF SHE HATES
ME FOR PRETENDING TO BE GAY?

11:39.323 --> 11:40.658
