TO SEPARATE US AGAIN.

11:40.741 --> 11:42.284
- THAT'S WHY YOU HAVE
TO TELL HER NOW

11:42.368 --> 11:43.994
BEFORE IT GETS OUT OF HAND.

11:44.078 --> 11:45.663
GOOD?
GOOD.

11:45.746 --> 11:46.956
- OKAY, THANKS, JOY.
YOU'RE A REALLY GOOD FRIEND.

11:47.039 --> 11:49.792
- YEAH, YEAH.

11:49.875 --> 11:50.584
[knocking at door]

11:56.048 --> 11:58.134
AHOY, CAPTAIN.

12:03.055 --> 12:04.473
