12:22.241 --> 12:23.659
- HERE YOU ARE.

12:23.742 --> 12:25.035
NOW OFF YOU GO BEFORE
YOU MISS YOUR MASSAGE.

12:25.119 --> 12:26.996
- YEAH, I THINK I DID MISS IT.

12:27.079 --> 12:30.291
