IN MY SHOWER?

13:04.783 --> 13:07.912
IN A LESS SEXY MAN,
THAT WOULD BE CREEPY.

13:07.995 --> 13:10.206
- YOU HAVE TO GET
RID OF YOUR WIFE.

13:10.289 --> 13:11.207
I'LL MEET YOU LATER.

13:11.290 --> 13:12.500
- FINE.
WHAT TIME?

13:12.583 --> 13:14.210
- SIX BELLS ON THE DOG WATCH?

13:14.293 --> 13:15.169
- WHEN?
- 1900 HOURS?

13:15.252 --> 13:16.712
- WHAT?

13:16.795 --> 13:20.174
- JUST FIND ME LATER.
