A LONG TIME.

13:50.329 --> 13:52.414
- OR, OR YOU COULD DO
AN ACTIVITY.

13:52.498 --> 13:53.707
- OR WE COULD DO ONE TOGETHER.

13:53.791 --> 13:55.584
